 人海茫茫，谢谢你，带我来到这里 ]</h2>\n        <p class=\"title-infor\">\n            <i class=\"point-header\"></i>光影留痕和半时咖啡<br>\n            <i class=\"point-header\"></i>一半咖啡一半红茶\n        </p>\n    </section>\n</header>\n        <section class=\"J_content content-body\"> \n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">街角宁静放空处</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_02.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>我在找寻合适的咖啡馆，模样淡定不惊慌，让我满载的</p>\n        <p>倦意可以找一座沙发的岛屿靠一靠。时间那么长</p>\n        <p>少有言语,我遇到了合我心意的咖啡屋子</p>\n        <p>藏住我的不开心</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">白-舒适的安全感</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_03.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>我喜欢这里洁白的墙壁，就算我知道一切白色的东西</p>\n        <p>都会慢慢变黑，可是依旧阻挡不了看到墙壁时</p>\n        <p>安全感满溢的内心</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">麻中微带一丝温柔</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_04.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>我喜欢这里麻布的沙发，瘟疫青年总是偏好这样的麻</p>\n        <p>那样的棉，也许这些都不是理由</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">书中自有颜如玉</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_05.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>我喜欢这里的满墙的阅读是多么温暖的事情</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">一滴馨香入口</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_06.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_07.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>我喜欢这里的食物，毕竟这里的每一样食物</p>\n        <p>都有一个好听的名字</p>\n        <p>这一杯咖啡叫做半时，那一壶茶叫光影留痕</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">回味世界百态</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_08.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_09.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>来来往往，日常会逐渐消化掉生活的戏剧性，</p>\n        <p>然后突然你想起了不开心的事</p>\n        <p>恩，不过没关系</p>\n        <p>跟我一起去这里坐坐吧</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"title\"><i class=\"lefticon\"></i><span class=\"subtitles\">居家懒虫首选</span><i class=\"righticon\"></i></h1>\n<h2 class=\"line-throw\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wapper-list\">\n    <ul class=\"J_piclist pic-list\">\n        <li class=\"pic-item\"><img src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_10.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\" alt=\"西塘\"></li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"describe\">\n        <p>生活很累，记得去喝咖啡</p>\n        <p>不想自制又想舒舒服服躺在家里享受美味</p>\n        <p>外带咖啡怎能错过</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n        \n\n        <div class=\"J_footer end-style\">\n    <h3 class=\"come-from\"><img class=\"icon-logo\" src=\"http://upp.tujiamedia.com/cafe/cafe_10.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/format/webp\"><span>图文来自图加摄影师 --</span> <i class=\"i\">团子酱</i></h3>\n    <p class=\"foot-world\">一个集美貌和文艺于一身的女子，关注图加公众号，有机会与园子酱一起去探寻杭城更多未知好店。</p>\n    <a class=\"J_goapp go-appbyid\" data-id=\"15651\"><i></i>进入图集</a>\n    <img class=\"img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">\n</div>\n\n    <section class=\"J_popview pop-view\"><div class=\"J_viewwapper wapper-view\"><ul class=\"J_imgview img-view\"></ul></div></section><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../../assets/libs/zepto.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../../assets/js/app/activities/beitang.js\"></script></body></html>', null, '\n        @font-face {\n            src: url(http://www.apple.com/wss/fonts/PingHei/v1/PingHei-light.woff) format(\"woff\"),url(http://www.apple.com/wss/fonts/PingHei/v1/PingHei-light.ttf) format(\"truetype\");\n        }\n\n        :focus,html * {\n            outline: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hidden,[class^=ads],[id^=ads] {\n            display: none!important;\n        }\n\n        sub,sup {\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        html {\n            color: #000;\n            background: #fff;\n            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n            text-size-adjust: 100%;\n        }\n\n        html * {\n            -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;\n            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\n        }\n\n        article,aside,blockquote,body,button,code,dd,details,div,dl,dt,fieldset,figcaption,figure,footer,form,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,header,hgroup,hr,input,legend,li,menu,nav,ol,p,pre,section,td,textarea,th,ul {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\